{"tid":1328972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄單嘢預示住一班人會收貨","createTime":"2019-07-18T05:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:23:18.000Z","uid":208722,"like":28,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"08294938935e5f5f6728434e76b5358d514a99d4","tid":1328972,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:25:43.000Z","msg":"明明已經唔係單單撤回修例可以解決到當今嘅問題<br />\n已經係正苦腐朽不堪，我哋要摧枯拉朽嘅事<br />\n點解無啦啦又要幫正苦諗點解決？<br />\n<br />\n我怕因為咁，啲人會開始<span style=\"color: red;\">妥協</span><br />\n到時7.21，或者往後只會更少人出嚟<br />\n所以要睇路，諗清楚係咪要咁就算<br />\n認真思考下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記住<br />\n佢有佢自己同正苦deal<br />\n我哋有我哋升級</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢一個人唔代表廣大市民</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9643b2e24a1650c1e40023649dba342dc78922","tid":1328972,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c20f481db7309f0a91186a802dee7e8d1b4d06b3","tid":1328972,"uid":209097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:29:33.000Z","msg":"政府唔會收貨 完"},{"pid":"c55c74abf8f5dd4ba88158e386ff3d2f96f99b6b","tid":1328972,"uid":89170,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"有紅字都冇用<br />\n<br />\n依家好多人就咁睇一睇完就話你分化<br />\n我頂住你走先"},{"pid":"5d5c7c6d9227e8e1273a6342e31bb1d1f2979431","tid":1328972,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"eace15ae0b3e15ce53e397f257d8d5367dfc9866","tid":1328972,"uid":89170,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"明明真係有班淺黃係覺得搞掂條例就等訴完咗件事<br />\n五大訴求都UP唔出<br />\n<br />\n一傾好就唔知會無咗幾多人<br />\n唔好淨係睇同溫層得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n講事實都叫分化 負評都唔講咩原因<br />\n成班連衛兵"},{"pid":"7cda8f09a70f9de9148775463ee62b18f6e3a65d","tid":1328972,"uid":277702,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:32:48.000Z